1)Finding Similar Items

  creteria might be many, and they can be many
  one naive way is to examine all the pairs

2)locality-sensitive hashing, or LSH

  avoid looking all pairs

3)Jaccard similarity = |S ∩ T |/|S ∪ T |   (common/all)

  If items can be seen as sets of things
  jaccard similarity is good way to find the similary

  *for example similar texts, similar customers (buy similar items)

